high_descs: Turn right, turn left, go towards counter.
Place bread into microwave, close door.
Open fridge door, place bread into fridge.
anns.task_desc: Get bread, cook bread, put bread into fridge.

high_descs: Turn around to the right and halfway turn left towards the stove. Make another left and walk towards the sink.
Pick up the loaf of bread sitting on the counter by the sink.
Turn around to walk towards the table then a quick right to the stove holding the bread up near the microwave.
Heat up the bread in the microwave and take it back out.
Turn around to walk to the door and make a left so you are standing in front of the fridge.
Open the fridge to put the bread on the shelf with the tomato and then shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Heat up a loaf of bread to put it away in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right and move towards the refrigerator next to the door then turn left and move towards the oven then turn right and move to the sink next to the rubbish bin.
Pick up the loaf of bread to the right of the lettuce from the corner of the counter.
Turn around and move towards the table with the stool in front of it then turn right and move to the oven.
Open the microwave above the oven, microwave the loaf of bread, then pick up the loaf of bread from the microwave. Close the microwave door.
Turn around and move towards the kitchen door and then turn right and move to the refrigerator in the corner of the room.
Place the loaf of bread to the right of the tomato on the top shelf in the refrigerator and close the refrigerator door.
anns.task_desc: Chill a warmed loaf of bread.
